sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant Routing as Routing Service
    participant Graph as Road Network Graph
    participant Traffic as Traffic Aggregator
    participant Phones as GPS Pings

    Note over Phones,Traffic: Continuous traffic ingest
    Phones-)Traffic: Anonymized GPS ping (every 30s)
    Traffic-)Traffic: Map-match to segment, 5-min window avg
    Traffic-)Graph: Update edge weights (smoothed speeds)

    Note over Client,Routing: Route request
    Client->>Routing: POST /route (origin, dest, mode)
    Routing->>Graph: Load CH-augmented region (in-memory)
    Routing->>Routing: Bidirectional Dijkstra on upward edges
    Routing-->>Client: { polyline, steps, ETA }

    Note over Client,Routing: Mid-trip re-route
    loop While navigating
        Client->>Client: Compare position to polyline
        alt Big deviation detected
            Client->>Routing: Request re-route
            Routing-->>Client: New polyline + ETA
        else On-route
            Client->>Client: Continue from cached polyline
        end
    end
